<para style="p">A psalm of David, when he fled from Absalom his son.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Yahweh, how many are my enemies!</para>

<para style="q1">Many have risen against me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Many say about me,</para>

<para style="q1">"There is no help for him from God."

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
